| Feature | Slimefun | Pylon | TechFactory | Best For You |
|---------|----------|-------|------------|-------------|
| **Addon System** | âœ… SlimefunAddon interface | âœ… PylonAddon | âŒ None | **COPY FROM SLIMEFUN** |
